(VERSION 1.1) (February 2010)

CS_Ship_TWS, a map by The Wormhole Studios

This is a older version and smaller version of this map, you can download the newer here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/126140

Preview of the map:
<object width="300"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/-XH_DSBACII&color1=0xb1b1b1&color2=0xcfcfcf&hl=en_US&feature=player_embedded&fs=1"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowScriptAccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/-XH_DSBACII&color1=0xb1b1b1&color2=0xcfcfcf&hl=en_US&feature=player_embedded&fs=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowfullscreen="true" allowScriptAccess="always" width="300"></embed></object>

It seems like there will be a FY_Ship_TWS and CS_Ship_Night, and probably a CS_Ship_V2 with more details...

------------------------------------
HOW TO INSTALL
------------------------------------

1. Put the files "cs_ship_tws.nav" & "cs_ship_tws" here:
"X:\Programs\Steam\SteamApps\ (account name) \counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

2. Start up Counter-Strike: Source and play CS_Ship_TWS !
